pps/2331070/extras/4d931fe0a9303d06f9ccb04c2186623e.poster.avif?t=1771103848\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/4d931fe0a9303d06f9ccb04c2186623e.webm?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/4d931fe0a9303d06f9ccb04c2186623e.mp4?t=1771103848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/ef5d7ba1408f3efa280a264fdb571c89.avif?t=1771103848\" width=616 height=142 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• The game is based on unadapted versions of fairytales and folktales with elements of what is perceived in modern culture as horror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• The narrator reads the tale in a South Russian dialect. The story is told in the same manner as in Russian villages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• The soundtrack is an original piece based on folk songs from the central and southern parts of Russia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• The built-in encyclopaedia of folk tale characters, demonic creatures, household items, customs and rituals was compiled with the help of a consulting folklorist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331070/extras/5641f10e6782eb2a9bfb570b996f2d2c.avif?t=1771103848\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p>",
